{"tid":1702080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屌你老母，警察終於認接獲強姦報案","createTime":"2019-11-09T13:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T14:24:14.000Z","uid":271123,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f044b26ecb310ae06c786a794c825490de89706e","tid":1702080,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:46:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1633054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1633054&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpkXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=43e5356b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1633054</a><br />\n<br />\n網上消息流傳指，一名女子早前在被捕後疑被警察性侵，並需到伊利沙伯醫院接受墮胎手術。警方回應傳媒查詢時表示，投訴警察課於上月22日收到一名律師代表報案，表示其當事人聲稱於9月27日在荃灣警署內被強姦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警方表示，由於指控嚴重，隨即將個案交由新界南總區重案組調查。截至目前，報案人的指控內容與調查結果並不脗合，警方會繼續調查相關指控。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，醫管局回應查詢時則指，不評論網上個別個案的傳言，並重申保障病人私隱的重要性，又呼籲公眾不要到醫院範圍集會，以及作非醫療有關的活動，以免影響服務運作。"},{"pid":"b2d2860c482ddce916ccc91cf41ef586f5f42591","tid":1702080,"uid":271123,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"又係自己人查自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />DLLM"},{"pid":"5a4a4045de9c2d704e91c9ee23d59b56b11a7dd2","tid":1702080,"uid":160693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5d0da9d614c2cd1a5bd8aa22721f351a4218e3","tid":1702080,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"[推到聽朝］星期日朝早10:30 中環和平紀念碑 Poppy Day紀念儀式 全人類出席！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702037</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討